176 A.3d 212 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. REINALDO GONZALEZ, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-383 September Term 2017

080167 November 30, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003679-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
